HEADWORD: Percutient
<hw>Per*cu"tient</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>percutiens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>percutere</ets>. See
<er>Percuss</er>.]</ety> <def>Striking; having the power of
striking.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>That which strikes, or has
